review: There are not enough words to describe how thankful we are for wonderful care during my pregnancy, labor & delivery. You've helped bring a perfect miracle into our lives and  We are grateful to have such a knowledgeable,and friendly doctor ....the trust i have for her is not explainable.....i love her so much....i have not seen a doctor taking so much care for her patients like her.....she have been always there for me on phone ,anytime in a day or even in night whenever i need her she is there for me 24/7...i can not have a healthy and best pregnancy with such a sweet daughter without her.....thankyou for always being with me....

review: One of the finest doctors that i came across in my life. She is so helpful and caring.  My wife and i were so worried during the course of pregnancy but she guided us all the way and resolved all our concerns, queries and issues and also relieved us whenever we faced any panic situation. My wife's delivery was so smooth that i would recommend everyone to go for her.  We cannot thank her enough for the exceptional level of care she has provided and this has been the most amazing moment in our life. Thankyou from the bottom of our hearts mam.
